ThicknessNotes: Collected along one line crossing the MTD. Not precise
SlopeGradientNotes: measured on 80 km, between 1 and 14 km from the landslide, in the downslope direction of the landslide
SlopeGradientHeadscarpNotes: Taken at the same location as the scarp height. Gradient varies along the perimeter of the entire landslide. The headscarp gradient is variable.
